# agent-os schema (Cursor)

This project uses the agent-os pattern. Read these at session start:

- @AGENTS.md — canonical schema (memory protocol, agent dispatch, rules table)
- @memory/STATE.md — current priorities and blockers
- @memory/learnings.md — past mistakes (don't repeat) and patterns

Then, based on the task, read on demand:

- @memory/wiki/INDEX.md → relevant wiki pages
- @memory/clients/*.md if a client task
- @agent-os/rules/<rule>.md when behavior is in question

Do not duplicate the schema content here. AGENTS.md is the source of truth.

When in doubt about how to behave: read AGENTS.md first.
